==Trivia==
*All the [[Rune god armour|god]], [[Rune trimmed armour|trimmed]], [[Rune heraldic armour|heraldic]], and [[Gilded equipment|gilded]] versions of rune have the same exact stats as regular rune, with the interesting exception of the god and trimmed variants of the rune kiteshield: these have a ranged attack bonus of -2, as opposed to the -3 stat shared by all the others. Apart from that, the only other difference is that God armour has a +1 [[Prayer bonus]] per piece.
*[[Rune claws]] and [[Rune thrownaxe|throwing axes]] are the only rune weapons to have a [[special attack]].
*When the concept of Rune armour was first developed, the initial colour was supposed to be purple, however this was later changed to teal.

